01:14:42,899 --> 01:14:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] koje onak ne može,

1152
01:14:44,380 --> 01:14:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] inače medicinski nestati.

1153
01:14:47,840 --> 01:14:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ja zovem nakon toga doktore za operaciju,

1154
01:14:55,800 --> 01:14:56,819
[SPEAKER_01] koje su me pripremali,

1155
01:14:56,819 --> 01:14:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno nazovem na taj odjel

1156
01:14:58,420 --> 01:14:59,899
[SPEAKER_01] i kažem sestri,

1157
01:15:00,199 --> 01:15:01,239
[SPEAKER_01] evo samo da vam javim,

1158
01:15:01,239 --> 01:15:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] jer ja sam malo još pričekala neko vrijeme,

1159
01:15:03,800 --> 01:15:06,819
[SPEAKER_01] još sam pričekala da se trudnoća malo razvije

1160
01:15:06,819 --> 01:15:11,939
[SPEAKER_01] i otišla još jednom izvadi taj beta HCG,

1161
01:15:11,939 --> 01:15:13,680
[SPEAKER_01] već je bio preko 25 tisuća,

1162
01:15:13,680 --> 01:15:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] ono raslo je baš onak lijepo po PS-u kako treba

1163
01:15:17,119 --> 01:15:21,680
[SPEAKER_01] i nazovem tada i kažem ja sam trudna

1164
01:15:21,680 --> 01:15:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] i želim otkazati operaciju,

1165
01:15:23,920 --> 01:15:26,020
[SPEAKER_01] jer nema razloga za operaciju,

1166
01:15:26,020 --> 01:15:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] znači nemam više tumore,

1167
01:15:27,720 --> 01:15:28,739
[SPEAKER_01] je Bog me izcijelio,

1168
01:15:29,020 --> 01:15:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] kao molim,

1169
01:15:30,220 --> 01:15:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] kao hvala Bogu,

1170
01:15:33,739 --> 01:15:35,479
[SPEAKER_01] pa koliko vam je beta HCG,

1171
01:15:35,479 --> 01:15:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] doktor još kao,

1172
01:15:36,619 --> 01:15:37,260
[SPEAKER_01] kaže sestra,

1173
01:15:37,260 --> 01:15:37,939
[SPEAKER_01] kao doktore,

1174
01:15:37,939 --> 01:15:39,340
[SPEAKER_01] doktor brzo,

1175
01:15:39,340 --> 01:15:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] inače je nedostupan na telefon,

1176
01:15:41,300 --> 01:15:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] ali sad je morao čući šta se dogodilo,

1177
01:15:44,239 --> 01:15:45,560
[SPEAKER_01] i ja kažem doktore,

1178
01:15:45,560 --> 01:15:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo ja sam trudna,

1179
01:15:47,000 --> 01:15:53,560
[SPEAKER_01] tak da ovaj beta HCG mi je 20 prek 25 tisuća,

1180
01:15:53,560 --> 01:15:55,600
[SPEAKER_01] sad kao šta sad,

1181
01:15:55,600 --> 01:15:57,560
[SPEAKER_01] ono s obzirom da imamo ovaj termin,

1182
01:15:57,560 --> 01:15:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] pa zovem onda za to,

1183
01:15:58,739 --> 01:15:59,560
[SPEAKER_01] za tu operaciju,

1184
01:16:01,500 --> 01:16:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] kao kakve vijesti,

1185
01:16:03,619 --> 01:16:06,020
[SPEAKER_01] evo samo onda otkazujemo operaciju,

1186
01:16:06,020 --> 01:16:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] ne vidimo se više nikad,

1187
01:16:07,300 --> 01:16:08,720
[SPEAKER_01] kaže doktore,

1188
01:16:08,720 --> 01:16:09,319
[UNKNOWN] super,

1189
01:16:10,100 --> 01:16:12,239
[SPEAKER_01] a meni hvala Bogu,

1190
01:16:12,239 --> 01:16:15,439
[SPEAKER_01] sestra je ono samo prokomentirala Bogu hvala,

1191
01:16:15,439 --> 01:16:20,720
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj, evo tu je onda dalje išla moja trudnoća,

1192
01:16:20,720 --> 01:16:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] i cijeli taj hod s Bogom polako,

1193
01:16:24,699 --> 01:16:27,579
[SPEAKER_01] i onda tu te moje društvene mreže,

1194
01:16:27,579 --> 01:16:28,840
[SPEAKER_01] meni se postavilo pitanje,

1195
01:16:28,840 --> 01:16:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] sad se vraćam onda da odgovorim na ovo tvoje,

1196
01:16:31,619 --> 01:16:34,220
[SPEAKER_01] meni je to sad sve već,

1197
01:16:34,220 --> 01:16:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] odlučila sam napraviti pauzu od svega,

1198
01:16:37,420 --> 01:16:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] i uzeti si vrijeme samo da budem u miru,

1199
01:16:40,100 --> 01:16:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] s Bogom, Biblijom,

1200
01:16:41,079 --> 01:16:42,979
[SPEAKER_01] u molitvama, u slavljenju,

1201
01:16:42,979 --> 01:16:47,979
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan sam doslovno samo čitala Novi Zavijet,

1202
01:16:47,979 --> 01:16:48,560
[SPEAKER_01] upijala,

1203
01:16:48,560 --> 01:16:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] znači doslovno progutala sam cijeli Novi Zavijet

1204
01:16:52,000 --> 01:16:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] u par tjedana,

1205
01:16:53,539 --> 01:16:56,439
[SPEAKER_01] jako, jako me to sve doticalo,

1206
01:16:56,439 --> 01:16:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] baš mi je puno Bog progovarao,

1207
01:16:58,239 --> 01:16:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] otkrivao o sebi,

1208
01:16:59,380 --> 01:17:02,680
[SPEAKER_01] o svemu što trebam znati u tom početku,

1209
01:17:02,680 --> 01:17:04,119
[SPEAKER_01] i ono svaki put,

1210
01:17:04,119 --> 01:17:05,939
[SPEAKER_01] i dan danas kad otvorim Bibliju,

1211
01:17:05,939 --> 01:17:08,060
[SPEAKER_01] opet mi je kao da nisam nikad čitala,

1212
01:17:08,060 --> 01:17:09,939
[SPEAKER_01] jer uvijek nešto novo progovarao.

1213
01:17:09,939 --> 01:17:11,180
[SPEAKER_01] doslovno živa.

1214
01:17:11,180 --> 01:17:15,159
[SPEAKER_01] I htjela sam i ponijeti tu malu Bibliju,

1215
01:17:15,159 --> 01:17:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] ali zaboravila je o danas.

1216
01:17:19,760 --> 01:17:24,979
[SPEAKER_01] i da, i tu sam htjela onda ispričati

1217
01:17:24,979 --> 01:17:26,739
[SPEAKER_01] još taj dio o samodruštvenim mrežama,

1218
01:17:26,739 --> 01:17:29,399
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam tražila Boga,

1219
01:17:29,399 --> 01:17:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] nek mi onda, nek me usmjeri,

1220
01:17:31,380 --> 01:17:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] šta sad s tim.

1221
01:17:32,279 --> 01:17:35,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam sad, tu sam shvatila da to je,

1222
01:17:35,140 --> 01:17:36,979
[SPEAKER_01] onak, čisto prazno,

1223
01:17:37,079 --> 01:17:38,220
[SPEAKER_01] prazno, isprazno.

1224
01:17:38,220 --> 01:17:40,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nema tu te punine,

1225
01:17:40,300 --> 01:17:43,319
[SPEAKER_01] to je bilo samo isključivo neka moja želja,

1226
01:17:43,319 --> 01:17:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] moji planovi,

1227
01:17:44,539 --> 01:17:45,399
[SPEAKER_01] moji ciljevi,

1228
01:17:45,399 --> 01:17:47,100
[SPEAKER_01] hedonizam,

1229
01:17:47,100 --> 01:17:48,899
[SPEAKER_01] bez Boga,

1230
01:17:48,899 --> 01:17:50,779
[SPEAKER_01] bez dubine.

1231
01:17:52,319 --> 01:17:55,520
[SPEAKER_01] nisam više vidjela put,

1232
01:17:55,520 --> 01:17:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] nisam sebe uopće više pronalazila

1233
01:17:57,859 --> 01:18:00,640
[SPEAKER_01] o tome da i dalje snimam se na putovanjima,

1234
01:18:00,640 --> 01:18:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] da snimam hrane, lokacije,

1235
01:18:03,539 --> 01:18:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] hotele, destinacije,

1236
01:18:04,720 --> 01:18:06,380
[SPEAKER_01] sve mi je to bilo baš isprazno.

1237
01:18:07,260 --> 01:18:08,720
[SPEAKER_01] I samo sam onda u molitvi,

1238
01:18:08,720 --> 01:18:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] ono, bila mjesecima,

1239
01:18:09,960 --> 01:18:11,680
[SPEAKER_01] nisam ništa objavljivala,

1240
01:18:11,680 --> 01:18:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] niti se javljala online

1241
01:18:14,260 --> 01:18:18,319
[SPEAKER_01] i tako mi je jedan dan Bog progovorio,

1242
01:18:18,319 --> 01:18:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] opet kroz čitanje,

1243
01:18:21,640 --> 01:18:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] ono, čitam Bibliju,

1244
01:18:23,699 --> 01:18:24,520
[SPEAKER_01] tražila sam Bože,

1245
01:18:24,520 --> 01:18:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] ono, reci mi šta dalje,

1246
01:18:26,260 --> 01:18:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] evo, šta da radim s tim društvenim mrežama,

1247
01:18:28,340 --> 01:18:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] šta da radim uopće nito sa životom,

1248
01:18:30,659 --> 01:18:31,899
[SPEAKER_01] koji je sljedeći korak

1249
01:18:31,899 --> 01:18:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] i tu mi je bilo oživjelo opet govori

1250
01:18:36,279 --> 01:18:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] i nemoj prestati,

1251
01:18:37,800 --> 01:18:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] ne boj se jer ja sam s tobom,

1252
01:18:39,920 --> 01:18:41,520
[SPEAKER_01] ništa ti se neće dogoditi

1253
01:18:41,520 --> 01:18:43,479
[SPEAKER_01] i, ono, neće te zadesiti zlo,

1254
01:18:43,479 --> 01:18:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] samo kao govori svjedoči.

1255
01:18:45,619 --> 01:18:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] I tu mi je bilo jasno,

1256
01:18:48,880 --> 01:18:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] okej Bože,

1257
01:18:49,539 --> 01:18:51,560
[SPEAKER_01] jasno mi sad da želiš

1258
01:18:51,560 --> 01:18:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] da ovom ne šutim,

1259
01:18:53,680 --> 01:18:55,220
[SPEAKER_01] da želiš da se,

1260
01:18:55,220 --> 01:18:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] ovo to je silno dijelo,

1261
01:18:57,260 --> 01:18:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] čudesno čuje,

1262
01:18:59,119 --> 01:19:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] da svi znaju,

1263
01:19:00,000 --> 01:19:01,279
[SPEAKER_01] da si ti iscijelitelj,

1264
01:19:01,279 --> 01:19:02,859
[SPEAKER_01] da si ti otkupitelj,

1265
01:19:02,859 --> 01:19:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] da si ti put istina i život

1266
01:19:04,539 --> 01:19:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] i to je doslovno meni postalo

1267
01:19:08,079 --> 01:19:11,979
[SPEAKER_01] kao neka ta moja misija osobna,

1268
01:19:11,979 --> 01:19:14,399
[SPEAKER_01] jer znam da mi Bog nije dao to čudo

1269
01:19:14,399 --> 01:19:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] i takav dar da bi o tome šutjela

1270
01:19:17,119 --> 01:19:18,779
[SPEAKER_01] i da bi to držala za sebe,

1271
01:19:18,779 --> 01:19:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se skrivala

1272
01:19:21,380 --> 01:19:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] i da bi to kao, eto,

1273
01:19:23,960 --> 01:19:25,779
[SPEAKER_01] bio neki moj osobni,

1274
01:19:25,779 --> 01:19:28,939
[SPEAKER_01] samo, mojo malo osobno čudo,

1275
01:19:28,939 --> 01:19:30,560
[SPEAKER_01] eto, koje treba držati za sebe,

1276
01:19:30,560 --> 01:19:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] jer vjera je osobna stvar,

1277
01:19:32,119 --> 01:19:33,020
[SPEAKER_01] što sam sto puta

1278
01:19:33,020 --> 01:19:34,680
[SPEAKER_01] poslje čula.

1279
01:19:34,680 --> 01:19:37,020
[SPEAKER_01] I, ovaj,

1280
01:19:37,020 --> 01:19:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] i tu ja odlučila progovorit,

1281
01:19:39,760 --> 01:19:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] šta se dogodilo,

1282
01:19:40,819 --> 01:19:42,060
[SPEAKER_01] i tu sam i snimila

1283
01:19:42,060 --> 01:19:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] kratko video svjedočanstvo,

1284
01:19:44,920 --> 01:19:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam ispričala

1285
01:19:45,800 --> 01:19:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] ukratko priču

1286
01:19:46,800 --> 01:19:49,039
[SPEAKER_01] i još jedan zanimljiv detalj

1287
01:19:49,039 --> 01:19:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] koji sam ispomenula

1288
01:19:50,359 --> 01:19:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] o tom videu,

1289
01:19:51,000 --> 01:19:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] da, znači,

1290
01:19:51,779 --> 01:19:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] trudnoća se dogodila

1291
01:19:53,220 --> 01:19:55,859
[SPEAKER_01] dan nakon molitve u Osijeku.

1292
01:19:55,859 --> 01:19:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] Znači...

1293
01:19:56,720 --> 01:19:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je ona izračun,

1294
01:19:59,199 --> 01:20:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] da, prema datumu začeća,

1295
01:20:01,079 --> 01:20:03,300
[SPEAKER_01] na, kad, ono,

1296
01:20:03,300 --> 01:20:05,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad mjere na ultrazvuku i to,

1297
01:20:05,039 --> 01:20:06,399
[SPEAKER_01] datum začeća,

1298
