[SPEAKER_01] i plus,

1299
01:20:06,880 --> 01:20:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] gledali smo pod danima

1300
01:20:08,840 --> 01:20:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo imali odnose

1301
01:20:09,880 --> 01:20:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] i sve jedino to bio,

1302
01:20:11,340 --> 01:20:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] točno taj dan,

1303
01:20:12,800 --> 01:20:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] znači je mogo biti

1304
01:20:13,579 --> 01:20:14,500
[SPEAKER_01] u tom periodu,

1305
01:20:14,500 --> 01:20:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] dan nakon...

1306
01:20:15,180 --> 01:20:16,159
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je to slučajno.

1307
01:20:16,159 --> 01:20:16,899
[SPEAKER_01] Slučajno,

1308
01:20:16,899 --> 01:20:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] sasvim slučajno.

1309
01:20:18,340 --> 01:20:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] I, evo, tu je,

1310
01:20:21,140 --> 01:20:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] tako krenuo jednostavno

1311
01:20:23,779 --> 01:20:24,579
[SPEAKER_01] taj moj put je,

1312
01:20:24,579 --> 01:20:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] gdje god mi se sad otvaraju vrata,

1313
01:20:26,720 --> 01:20:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] znam da moram ić svijedočiti,

1314
01:20:28,239 --> 01:20:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam inače veliki tremaš

1315
01:20:29,859 --> 01:20:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] pred kamerama,

1316
01:20:30,760 --> 01:20:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] ali svaki put samo se molim,

1317
01:20:33,180 --> 01:20:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, ti progovaraj kroz mene,

1318
01:20:34,739 --> 01:20:38,979
[SPEAKER_01] znam da ćeš ti jednostavno naći način

1319
01:20:38,979 --> 01:20:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] da se proslavljaš

1320
01:20:40,220 --> 01:20:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] i kroz moju tremu

1321
01:20:43,579 --> 01:20:45,600
[SPEAKER_01] i kroz sve moje prepreke,

1322
01:20:45,600 --> 01:20:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači to je sve ništa

1323
01:20:47,739 --> 01:20:48,979
[SPEAKER_01] u usporedbi sa ovom,

1324
01:20:48,979 --> 01:20:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] sa tim što,

1325
01:20:52,500 --> 01:20:53,880
[SPEAKER_01] znači sa činjenicom

1326
01:20:53,880 --> 01:20:56,140
[SPEAKER_01] o čudu koje si napravio

1327
01:20:56,140 --> 01:20:56,819
[SPEAKER_01] u mom životu

1328
01:20:56,819 --> 01:20:57,439
[SPEAKER_01] i sa tim što

1329
01:20:57,439 --> 01:20:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] možeš napraviti

1330
01:20:59,840 --> 01:21:00,899
[SPEAKER_01] u životima drugih

1331
01:21:00,899 --> 01:21:02,439
[SPEAKER_01] koji ti se iskreno predaju

1332
01:21:02,439 --> 01:21:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] i koji te traže.

1333
01:21:03,340 --> 01:21:03,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je,

1334
01:21:03,859 --> 01:21:04,560
[SPEAKER_00] kako smo i rekli,

1335
01:21:04,560 --> 01:21:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] prije iskreno otvoreno srce,

1336
01:21:06,460 --> 01:21:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin stvarno neće

1337
01:21:08,119 --> 01:21:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] zaobići,

1338
01:21:09,159 --> 01:21:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] zanemariti,

1339
01:21:09,659 --> 01:21:12,100
[SPEAKER_00] neću tebe kao idem na drugoga.

1340
01:21:12,100 --> 01:21:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno je važno svjedočiti

1341
01:21:14,500 --> 01:21:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] i ljudi vole slušati svjedočanstva

1342
01:21:15,899 --> 01:21:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] jer na neki način onda i raste vjera.

1343
01:21:17,739 --> 01:21:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ono kao poboži,

1344
01:21:18,739 --> 01:21:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako si mogao njoj,

1345
01:21:19,579 --> 01:21:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] možeš i meni.

1346
01:21:20,340 --> 01:21:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] Voljela bih sad da za kraj

1347
01:21:23,460 --> 01:21:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] malo se samo još vratimo

1348
01:21:24,539 --> 01:21:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] na tu neplodnost.

1349
01:21:26,300 --> 01:21:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] Taj trenutak zapravo

1350
01:21:27,800 --> 01:21:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad ste vi kao bračni par,

1351
01:21:29,159 --> 01:21:31,359
[SPEAKER_00] koji, ok, možda nije sad bio cilj,

1352
01:21:31,359 --> 01:21:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] ono sad ne znam,

1353
01:21:32,000 --> 01:21:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] djeca i da vam je to bio

1354
01:21:33,039 --> 01:21:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] onako visoki prioritet.

1355
01:21:34,619 --> 01:21:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali taj trenutak,

1356
01:21:36,420 --> 01:21:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] ono, osjećaj jedno pred drugim.

1357
01:21:38,260 --> 01:21:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, možda je se osjećala ti

1358
01:21:41,380 --> 01:21:43,640
[SPEAKER_00] kao da te on razočarao,

1359
01:21:43,640 --> 01:21:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] iznevjerio,

1360
01:21:44,159 --> 01:21:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao kako si ti sad neplodan.

1361
01:21:45,579 --> 01:21:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] S druge strane,

1362
01:21:46,739 --> 01:21:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] i ti imaš tu diagnozu.

1363
01:21:48,159 --> 01:21:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] Neki sram ili nešto,

1364
01:21:50,079 --> 01:21:51,479
[SPEAKER_00] pitam jer mislim da se

1365
01:21:51,479 --> 01:21:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] mnogi parovi se bore

1366
01:21:53,619 --> 01:21:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] s neplodnošću, nažalost.

1367
01:21:54,680 --> 01:21:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] I možda se premalo priča

1368
01:21:56,760 --> 01:21:57,939
[SPEAKER_00] o tom pritisku

1369
01:21:57,939 --> 01:22:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] koju onda jedni drugima stvaramo,

1370
01:22:00,279 --> 01:22:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] htjeli, ne htjeli.

1371
01:22:02,000 --> 01:22:03,399
[SPEAKER_00] Moji suprug i ja smo

1372
01:22:03,399 --> 01:22:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] na neki način slično prošli

1373
01:22:05,039 --> 01:22:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] nakon prvog djeteta.

1374
01:22:05,880 --> 01:22:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je on imao deset mjeseci,

1375
01:22:07,140 --> 01:22:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] sam imala van materničnu trudnoću.

1376
01:22:09,640 --> 01:22:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ni znala da sam trudna.

1377
01:22:11,260 --> 01:22:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, sasvim slučajno,

1378
01:22:12,539 --> 01:22:13,899
[SPEAKER_00] zbog ogromnih,

1379
01:22:13,899 --> 01:22:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] užasnih bolova po noći.

1380
01:22:15,180 --> 01:22:15,699
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

1381
01:22:15,699 --> 01:22:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ujutro smo otišli na hitnu.

1382
01:22:17,840 --> 01:22:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] Još me doslovno natjerao suprug

1383
01:22:19,960 --> 01:22:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisam mogla ni čučnuti,

1384
01:22:21,239 --> 01:22:22,319
[SPEAKER_00] nisam se mogla ni ispraviti.

1385
01:22:22,319 --> 01:22:23,279
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko me sve boljilo,

1386
01:22:23,279 --> 01:22:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] ono, baš grozno.

1387
01:22:24,180 --> 01:22:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] I otišli na hitnu.

1388
01:22:26,539 --> 01:22:28,180
[SPEAKER_00] ja, ono, doslovno sam došla

1389
01:22:28,180 --> 01:22:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] skoro u zadnji čas.

1390
01:22:29,619 --> 01:22:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] Hitna operacija,

1391
01:22:31,279 --> 01:22:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad su skužili šta je,

1392
01:22:32,500 --> 01:22:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] sve ono, pretrage.

1393
01:22:33,319 --> 01:22:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] To nisu mi mogli ni krv izvaditi.

1394
01:22:34,819 --> 01:22:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko su mi sužene već bile žile

1395
01:22:37,279 --> 01:22:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] zbog unutarne krvaranja

1396
01:22:38,340 --> 01:22:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] jer je prsnuo jajovod.

1397
01:22:39,500 --> 01:22:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ni znala.

1398
01:22:40,720 --> 01:22:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se tog trenutka

1399
01:22:42,619 --> 01:22:44,520
[SPEAKER_00] kad me baš, ono, brutalno zaboljilo.

1400
01:22:44,520 --> 01:22:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, ne znam šta je.

1401
01:22:45,840 --> 01:22:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] To misla kamenci možda,

1402
01:22:46,920 --> 01:22:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili nešto, nemam pojma.

1403
01:22:47,880 --> 01:22:50,180
[SPEAKER_00] I operacija je, ono,

1404
01:22:50,180 --> 01:22:52,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad su mi rekli da su izvadili jajovod

1405
01:22:52,239 --> 01:22:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] i sve i da su provjerili drugi jajovod,

1406
01:22:54,340 --> 01:22:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] da je začepljen,

1407
01:22:55,380 --> 01:22:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] kontrast nije prošao

1408
01:22:56,539 --> 01:22:57,640
[SPEAKER_00] i kao da vrlo vjerojatno

1409
01:22:57,640 --> 01:22:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] nećemo više moći imati biološke djece.

1410
01:22:59,960 --> 01:23:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, kao odjednom.

1411
01:23:02,619 --> 01:23:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, nisam ni znala da sam trudna.

1412
01:23:04,640 --> 01:23:06,520
[SPEAKER_00] Sad saznala da sam izgubila djete.

1413
01:23:06,520 --> 01:23:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] Grozno, da.

1414
01:23:07,340 --> 01:23:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, samo tako ti kažu

1415
01:23:10,279 --> 01:23:11,779
[SPEAKER_00] nećete više moći imati djece.

1416
01:23:11,779 --> 01:23:13,319
[SPEAKER_00] A i prvo djete, ono,

1417
01:23:13,319 --> 01:23:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] prošlo je godinu dana

1418
01:23:14,699 --> 01:23:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] da smo ga uspjeli začiti,

1419
01:23:16,579 --> 01:23:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] a da smo baš ciljali plodne dane.

1420
01:23:18,159 --> 01:23:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

1421
01:23:19,340 --> 01:23:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, odjednom ti se sruši to sve.

1422
01:23:21,119 --> 01:23:25,020
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ti trenuci naših razgovora,

1423
01:23:25,020 --> 01:23:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno jednog razgovora,

1424
01:23:26,680 --> 01:23:29,520
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo nekog izbjegavali to,

1425
01:23:29,520 --> 01:23:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja sam osjećala sram.

1426
01:23:31,739 --> 01:23:33,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se pitala,

1427
01:23:33,439 --> 01:23:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] ono, hoće li on sad mene manje voljet?

1428
01:23:36,079 --> 01:23:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kao u meni je problem.

1429
01:23:37,699 --> 01:23:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu imati djece.

1430
01:23:38,840 --> 01:23:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] On je, očito, i dalje plodan,

1431
01:23:41,159 --> 01:23:42,560
[SPEAKER_00] ono, ako smo uspjeli prvo djete.

1432
01:23:42,560 --> 01:23:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] A sad je u meni problem, ono,

1433
01:23:44,340 --> 01:23:46,520
[SPEAKER_00] što će sad biti s našim odnosom?

1434
01:23:46,520 --> 01:23:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] On sanja veliku obitelj.

1435
01:23:48,199 --> 01:23:50,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, stalno govori o četvero-petero djece,

1436
01:23:50,479 --> 01:23:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] ono, mini-nogometna ekipica.

1437
01:23:52,220 --> 01:23:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zajedno smo zapravo to sanjali,

1438
01:23:55,119 --> 01:23:56,060
[SPEAKER_00] ono, uvukome u to.

1439
01:23:56,060 --> 01:23:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] I misli si, kako sad?

1440
01:23:58,859 --> 01:24:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ću ja sad pred njega stati onak reći,

1441
01:24:01,359 --> 01:24:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu ti dati više djece.

1442
01:24:03,319 --> 01:24:06,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu ispuniti svoju svrhu, je li nešto.

1443
01:24:06,439 --> 01:24:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, i u vjeri isto,

1444
01:24:08,359 --> 01:24:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] kao kako to mislite, imate samo jedno djete.

1445
01:24:10,199 --> 01:24:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] Često bude taj malo pritisak.

1446
01:24:13,119 --> 01:24:15,600
[SPEAKER_00] Mi, ono, željeli smo imati više djece

1447
01:24:15,600 --> 01:24:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] i sve to nekako i prirodno dođe.

1448
01:24:17,119 --> 01:24:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] Baš sam osjećala te neki sram i pritisak

1449
01:24:19,220 --> 01:24:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] i težinu i brigu za naš odnos.

1450
01:24:21,159 --> 01:24:23,060
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ću ja sad njega u oči pogledat?

1451
01:24:23,060 --> 01:24:24,479
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ćemo mi dalje imati odnose?

1452
01:24:24,479 --> 01:24:28,479
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo da ne može završiti trudnoćom.

1453
01:24:28,479 --> 01:24:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] I to mi je baš bilo onako teško,

1454
01:24:30,840 --> 01:24:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] ali smo izbjegavali taj razgovor.

1455
01:24:32,699 --> 01:24:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, čvrsti smo mi, ok, nema veze.

1456
01:24:34,739 --> 01:24:36,600
[SPEAKER_00] Biće sve dobro, ono, kako će biti sve dobro?

1457
01:24:36,600 --> 01:24:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ne procesuiraš, ne radiš, ne moliš za to?

1458
01:24:39,279 --> 01:24:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] I sve to.

1459
01:24:40,880 --> 01:24:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] I isto su, kad sam odišla na jedan pregled,

1460
01:24:43,279 --> 01:24:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] jer su kao na toj drugoj strani,

1461
01:24:46,079 --> 01:24:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] isto bila kao vodena cista

1462
01:24:47,760 --> 01:24:50,939
[SPEAKER_00] i sad jedan doktor je rekao da je to veliki problem.

1463
01:24:50,939 --> 01:24:54,520
[SPEAKER_00] Išla sam u bolnicu na pregled

1464
01:24:54,520 --> 01:24:57,640
[SPEAKER_00] i prvo što mi je rekla doktorica je bilo

1465
01:24:57,640 --> 01:25:00,300
[SPEAKER_00] kao pa vi ste savršen kandidat za potpomognutu oplodnju.

1466
01:25:00,300 --> 01:25:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nije me ni pregledala, ni ultrazvuk,

1467
01:25:02,039 --> 01:25:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] ni čula cijelu diagnozu, sve što se događalo.

1468
01:25:04,920 --> 01:25:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onak ne, nismo jer ne želimo.

1469
01:25:07,619 --> 01:25:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno to nije naš put

1470
01:25:10,159 --> 01:25:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] i nije niti u skladu s našom vjerom, uvjerenjima,

1471
01:25:12,579 --> 01:25:14,060
[SPEAKER_00] željom uopće.

1472
01:25:14,060 --> 01:25:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je stvarno tako, ne znam, posvojit ćemo ili nešto.

1473
01:25:16,460 --> 01:25:19,720
[SPEAKER_00] I da skratim, uspjela sam ju nagovoriti

1474
01:25:19,720 --> 01:25:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] da me pregleda ultrazvukom,

1475
01:25:21,739 --> 01:25:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] onda je zaključila je to samo ta vodena cista

1476
01:25:23,539 --> 01:25:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] da nema nikakav uticaj,

1477
01:25:24,699 --> 01:25:27,560
[SPEAKER_00] da bi trebalo biti sve u redu i sa ono olakšanje.

1478
01:25:27,560 --> 01:25:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se otvorio put vjere neki.

1479
01:25:29,279 --> 01:25:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] I mi razgovarali i kad smo skinuli taj teret neki

1480
01:25:32,619 --> 01:25:34,899
[SPEAKER_00] zašto uopće želimo imati još djece

1481
01:25:34,899 --> 01:25:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] i da je u redu ako nemamo,

1482
01:25:36,640 --> 01:25:38,479
[SPEAKER_00] ako je to stvarno Božja volja za naš život,

1483
01:25:38,479 --> 01:25:40,060
[SPEAKER_00] onda ćemo slijediti njegovu volju

1484
01:25:40,060 --> 01:25:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako je volja da posvojimo ili nešto.

1485
01:25:42,079 --> 01:25:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] I na zajednici se isto molilo puno za to

1486
01:25:45,420 --> 01:25:47,560
[SPEAKER_00] i sjećam se je biletavan pjesma na susretu

1487
01:25:47,560 --> 01:25:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] ono put stvara čudači i reći svoju drži.

1488
01:25:49,859 --> 01:25:52,239
[SPEAKER_00] I kužiš kao put stvara, put kroz jajovod.

1489
01:25:52,239 --> 01:25:53,060
[SPEAKER_00] To je moja pjesma.

1490
01:25:53,060 --> 01:25:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] I ja ono da sam plakala na tom susretu

1491
01:25:57,859 --> 01:26:00,239
[SPEAKER_00] i poslije sam otišla privatno

1492
01:26:00,239 --> 01:26:01,680
[SPEAKER_00] na propuhivanje jajovoda.

1493
01:26:01,680 --> 01:26:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ono, ok, bog, molitva, sve super,

1494
01:26:04,119 --> 01:26:06,319
[SPEAKER_00] ali moraš i ti nešto konkretno očiniti.

1495
01:26:06,319 --> 01:26:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] I otišla sam privatno,

1496
01:26:07,659 --> 01:26:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] doktor je bio predobar

1497
01:26:08,720 --> 01:26:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] i sve mi je objasnio,

1498
01:26:10,380 --> 01:26:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] vodio me kroz to ja cijelo vrijeme u sebi pjevala

1499
01:26:12,500 --> 01:26:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] samo tu pjesmu, pjela pjesmu

1500
01:26:13,960 --> 01:26:15,859
[SPEAKER_00] i on kao, evo, pogledajte sada na ekrani,

1501
01:26:15,859 --> 01:26:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] gledamo mi kontrast kako prolazi

1502
01:26:17,659 --> 01:26:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže sve, evo, sve je to lijepo prolazio.

1503
01:26:19,739 --> 01:26:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, sve sam bože, ono.

1504
01:26:21,159 --> 01:26:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ne mogu vjerovat, molim za to,

1505
01:26:23,000 --> 01:26:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] onda ime ne mogu vjerovat.

1506
01:26:24,279 --> 01:26:26,560
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi ispalo na kraju,

1507
01:26:26,560 --> 01:26:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] rekao je da sam u fazi skroz pred ovulaciju

1508
01:26:32,399 --> 01:26:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao je ništa, svaka dva dana odnose sad

1509
01:26:34,659 --> 01:26:36,720
[SPEAKER_00] i ono, vidjet ćemo, jel?

1510
01:26:36,720 --> 01:26:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] I odmah taj prvi mjesec sam ostala trudna.

1511
01:26:39,739 --> 01:26:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] Odlično, slava Bogu.

1512
01:26:41,140 --> 01:26:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] David sad ima dvije godine.

1513
01:26:43,100 --> 01:26:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] S tim da sam vjerojatno već bila trudna,

1514
01:26:45,579 --> 01:26:49,399
[SPEAKER_00] to jest, ono, doslovno dva dana nakon

1515
01:26:49,399 --> 01:26:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] što sam bila na tom pregledu

1516
01:26:50,739 --> 01:26:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] i što smo imali odnose,

1517
01:26:51,779 --> 01:26:53,060
[SPEAKER_00] sam ja imala svjedočanstvo,

1518
01:26:53,060 --> 01:26:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] to jest temu sam pričala na susretu zajednice

1519
01:26:55,739 --> 01:26:58,020
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerujem da je već tada i došla do začeća.

1520
01:26:58,020 --> 01:27:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo pjevali i tu pjesmu ponovno,

1521
01:27:00,500 --> 01:27:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] put stvara i sve,

1522
01:27:01,420 --> 01:27:02,760
[SPEAKER_00] to mi je bilo onako baš poveznica.

1523
01:27:02,760 --> 01:27:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali taj dio, kako ste vi prošli to ovoga,

1524
01:27:05,539 --> 01:27:07,439
[SPEAKER_00] taj osjećaj težine, srama,

1525
01:27:07,439 --> 01:27:11,479
[SPEAKER_00] eventualno, ono, ste uspjeli to iskomunicirati i prihvatiti, jel?

1526
01:27:11,479 --> 01:27:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pa, meni je nekako ovakotna okolnost bila taj,

1527
01:27:16,079 --> 01:27:22,199
[SPEAKER_01] što Luka, on i nije htio, nije uopće bio previše zainteresiran,

1528
01:27:22,199 --> 01:27:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] da mi imamo djecu,

1529
01:27:23,199 --> 01:27:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer smo bili u tom cijelom nekom svom fokusu na sebe,

1530
01:27:27,300 --> 01:27:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] na uživanje u životu, na putovanja.

1531
01:27:29,619 --> 01:27:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo nam je dobro tad, u tom periodu,

1532
01:27:33,500 --> 01:27:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] kao zašto da si sad, narušavamo mir i sve ostalo.

1533
01:27:38,380 --> 01:27:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] Cijela ta nekao biti, sebična neka slika,

1534
01:27:43,380 --> 01:27:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] makar kao gledali smo, pa zašto, pa nije to neka drama.

1535
01:27:47,199 --> 01:27:51,100
[SPEAKER_01] I sad onda kad smo saznali, evo, da ne možemo imati djete,

1536
01:27:51,100 --> 01:27:53,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam u biti isplakala to.

1537
01:27:53,779 --> 01:27:56,939
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo mi je, pa kao, zašto ja sad plaćem?

1538
01:27:57,300 --> 01:28:00,180
[SPEAKER_01] A i onako nisam htjela djete još,

1539
01:28:00,180 --> 01:28:05,439
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi je, aha, ok, možda sam htjela malo u nekom kasnijem periodu,

1540
01:28:05,439 --> 01:28:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] barem imat opciju da imam djete i ono, kad zaželim da mogu.

1541
01:28:10,699 --> 01:28:14,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nekako brzo smo prešli preko svega toga

1542
01:28:14,020 --> 01:28:16,140
[SPEAKER_01] i baš smo pričali, pa gle, nije drama,

1543
01:28:16,140 --> 01:28:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] oboje smo neplodni, očito to nije naš put.

1544
01:28:20,500 --> 01:28:23,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ćemo htjeti imati djecu, naći ćemo put.

1545
01:28:23,600 --> 01:28:27,020
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji puno djeca koje čekaju da ih se posvoji.

1546
01:28:27,300 --> 01:28:30,920
[SPEAKER_01] I s tim smo se nekako pomirili, nismo htjeli forsirati ništa

1547
01:28:30,920 --> 01:28:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] i s te strane, evo, meni je bilo lakše,

1548
01:28:34,460 --> 01:28:37,779
[SPEAKER_01] jer nisam osjećala nikakvu osudu ni odluke,

1549
01:28:37,779 --> 01:28:43,020
[SPEAKER_01] niti sam ja imala prema njemu neka očekivanja

1550
01:28:43,020 --> 01:28:48,420
[SPEAKER_01] i da mi je bilo žao sad zato što je u takvoj situaciji.

1551
01:28:48,420 --> 01:28:54,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ali jednostavno, evo, bili smo si nekak podrška u tom,

1552
01:28:54,899 --> 01:28:56,840
[SPEAKER_01] jer smo bili na istoj valnoj duljini,

1553
01:28:56,840 --> 01:28:59,640
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo, ne znam šta bi iskreno rekla parovima.

1554
01:28:59,640 --> 01:29:04,520
[SPEAKER_01] Da, iskomunicirali jesmo i to je bitno.

1555
01:29:04,520 --> 01:29:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] Bitno je da nema tih zamjerki koje se guraju pod tepih,

1556
01:29:08,420 --> 01:29:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] jer sve što se zamjera i preko toga prelazi,

1557
01:29:12,640 --> 01:29:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad tad će isplivati kroz neke još veće probleme.

1558
01:29:17,260 --> 01:29:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] i jako je važna komunikacija u braku zapravo.

1559
01:29:20,239 --> 01:29:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] A vi ste zapravo cijeli svoj odnos temeljili nekako

1560
01:29:23,800 --> 01:29:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] na tim nekim vrijednostima koje su onako duboko ukorjenjene

1561
01:29:28,119 --> 01:29:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo u Bogu i ne znajući.

1562
01:29:30,039 --> 01:29:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1563
01:29:30,199 --> 01:29:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jer eto, vraćamo se opet na to otvoreno srce,

1564
01:29:32,659 --> 01:29:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] koje je tvoje srce koje je uvijek tražilo,

1565
01:29:34,739 --> 01:29:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] a vjerujem da si tom svojom otvorenošću i njega potaknula,

1566
01:29:38,340 --> 01:29:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] jer eto, ti si njegova izabranica i volite

1567
01:29:41,659 --> 01:29:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] i najbolja si mu prijateljica i partnerica i sve

1568
01:29:45,199 --> 01:29:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako koliko je onda važno biti tako otvoren,

1569
01:29:49,260 --> 01:29:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] jer Bog onda djeluje, a da ti ni ne znaš.

1570
01:29:51,039 --> 01:29:51,439
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je.

1571
01:29:51,439 --> 01:29:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ti doslovno nisi u tim trenutcima još bila potpuno obraćena,

1572
01:29:54,880 --> 01:29:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] kao malo si se još otvarala više,

1573
01:29:56,800 --> 01:29:59,640
[SPEAKER_00] a već tada je on kroz tebe mijenjao i njego srce

1574
01:29:59,640 --> 01:30:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] i pripremao teren za sve ono što je slijedilo.

1575
01:30:01,579 --> 01:30:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je baš fascinantno.

1576
01:30:03,779 --> 01:30:06,279
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i meni je baš to što kažeš je,

1577
01:30:06,279 --> 01:30:08,640
[SPEAKER_01] kad sad gledam iz te šire perspektive,

1578
01:30:08,640 --> 01:30:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidim da je to neki cijeli Božji plan veći bio,

1579
01:30:13,140 --> 01:30:17,899
[SPEAKER_01] što on naravno radi iz perspektive da zna već

1580
01:30:17,899 --> 01:30:20,760
[SPEAKER_01] šta će se dogoditi, kad će se dogoditi,

1581
01:30:20,760 --> 01:30:23,720
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način će stvari posložiti,

1582
01:30:23,720 --> 01:30:29,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi ne vidimo u toj određenoj situaciji.

1583
01:30:29,699 --> 01:30:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] Isto kao što je on tek sad iz ove perspektive,

1584
01:30:32,539 --> 01:30:36,060
[SPEAKER_01] vidim i sve te situacije koje su se morale posložiti,

1585
01:30:36,060 --> 01:30:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno koje je Bog posložio,

1586
01:30:37,460 --> 01:30:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] da jednostavno budem spremna doći do te spoznaje

1587
01:30:44,300 --> 01:30:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] o njemu do koje sam došla,

1588
01:30:46,659 --> 01:30:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] a i tu vidim da baš radi puno na Lukinom srcu.

1589
01:30:50,079 --> 01:30:56,479
[SPEAKER_01] On, ne mogu reći da je još na fazi na toj duhovnoj spoznaji

1590
01:30:56,479 --> 01:31:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] na kojoj sam ja, ali je toliko se otvorio Bogu već

1591
01:31:00,420 --> 01:31:06,180
[SPEAKER_01] da je to meni neprepoznatljivo usporedbi s onim starim Lukom.

1592
01:31:06,920 --> 01:31:10,600
[SPEAKER_01] Vidim da otvoren je više, otvoren je za molitve,

1593
01:31:10,600 --> 01:31:12,779
[SPEAKER_01] otvoren je za sve o Bogu što mu pričam,

1594
01:31:12,779 --> 01:31:16,319
[SPEAKER_01] za zajedničko čitanje Biblije,

1595
01:31:16,319 --> 01:31:18,600
[SPEAKER_01] molimo se prije obroka zajedno,

1596
01:31:18,600 --> 01:31:20,439
[SPEAKER_01] molimo se prije spavanja zajedno.

1597
01:31:20,439 --> 01:31:23,840
[SPEAKER_01] To su mi stvari koje sam mislila u početku,

1598
01:31:23,840 --> 01:31:27,060
[SPEAKER_01] pa ovo je nemoguće, nikad se to neće dogoditi u našem braku,

1599
01:31:27,060 --> 01:31:32,140
[SPEAKER_01] a događa se i baš mi puno znače takve stvari,

1600
01:31:32,140 --> 01:31:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer vidim doslovno pred svojim očima

1601
01:31:35,340 --> 01:31:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] vidim da se promjena događa

1602
01:31:37,539 --> 01:31:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] i da je ono pitanje dana kada će stvarno doći

1603
01:31:41,079 --> 01:31:43,279
[SPEAKER_01] do te spozna gdje sam ja.

1604
01:31:43,279 --> 01:31:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, i kada ne vidim i tada radiš.

1605
01:31:46,000 --> 01:31:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

1606
01:31:46,800 --> 01:31:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je rekla Simona u podcastu

1607
01:31:48,779 --> 01:31:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je silan, ali nije nasilan.

1608
01:31:50,579 --> 01:31:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] On poštuje slobodu Luke,

1609
01:31:52,840 --> 01:31:56,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali onako nježno ga vraća k sebi.

1610
01:31:56,180 --> 01:32:00,100
[SPEAKER_00] Monika, mi bi mogli još dva sata razgovarati,

1611
01:32:00,100 --> 01:32:01,979
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da smo iscrpile sve baterije

1612
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] i sve memoriske kartice Tomom i ovdje u stresu.

1613
01:32:05,340 --> 01:32:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ćemo lagano završiti.

1614
01:32:08,279 --> 01:32:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti na ovom prekrasnom razgovoru,

1615
01:32:10,739 --> 01:32:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] svjedočenju i kavi i čaju koji smo gledali.

1616
01:32:14,619 --> 01:32:18,699
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, ako možeš samo za kraj još neku poruku

1617
01:32:18,699 --> 01:32:21,979
[SPEAKER_00] ženama koje gledaju nešto što ti je na srcu.

1618
01:32:22,159 --> 01:32:26,220
[SPEAKER_01] Može. Pa evo, od samog početka mi je na srcu poruka

1619
01:32:26,220 --> 01:32:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] koju nosim na majci i na naučnicama.

1620
01:32:30,079 --> 01:32:36,020
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ovo je majca na kojoj piše, evo možeš pročiti.

1621
01:32:36,020 --> 01:32:37,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav s neba sišla je.

1622
01:32:37,319 --> 01:32:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ljubav s neba sišla je i ne znam ili se vidi,

1623
01:32:40,239 --> 01:32:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači, Bog koji izljeva ljubav,

1624
01:32:42,960 --> 01:32:47,140
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno kišu milosti na nas.

1625
01:32:47,140 --> 01:32:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] I na naučnicama, znači, Ivan 3.16,

1626
01:32:53,119 --> 01:32:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] jer je Bog tako ljubio svijet da je dao svog jedinorođenog sina

1627
01:32:58,159 --> 01:33:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] da spasi, da sve koji vjeruju ne propadno,

1628
01:33:04,739 --> 01:33:06,300
[SPEAKER_01] nego da ih spasi.

1629
01:33:06,300 --> 01:33:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] I njegova ljubljena, znači, ti si njegova ljubljena

1630
01:33:12,640 --> 01:33:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] i on te zove, isto kao što je mene zvao,

1631
01:33:16,560 --> 01:33:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] samo mu otvori svoje srce i dopusti da radi.

1632
01:33:21,619 --> 01:33:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, što više reći nego amen.

1633
01:33:24,619 --> 01:33:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] Boži blagoslov svima.

